Package: aces
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Constrained Enveloping Splines
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  person(
    given = "Víctor J.", 
    family = "España", 
    email = "vespana@umh.es",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1807-6180"))
Description: Functions are provided to determine production frontiers and technical 
    efficiency measures through non-parametric techniques based upon multivariate adaptive
    regression splines. The package includes code for estimating production frontiers and
    computing efficiency scores through radial input, output, directional and additive measures.
